erty global is the world’s largest international tv and broadband company with operations in more than  countries across europe latin america and the caribbean we invest in the infrastructure that empowers our customers to make the most of the digital revolution our scale and commitment to innovation enable us to develop marketleading products delivered through nextgeneration networks that connect our  million customers who subscribe to over  million television broadband internet and telephony services we also serve over  million mobile subscribers and offer wifi service across  million access points liberty global’s businesses are comprised of two stocks the liberty global group nasdaq lbtya lbtyb and lbtyk for our european operations and the lilac group nasdaq lila and lilak otc link lilab which consists of our operations in latin america and the caribbean the liberty global group operates in  european countries under the consumer brands virgin media unitymedia telenet and upc the liberty global group also owns  of vodafoneziggo a dutch joint venture which has  million customers  million fixedline subscribers and  million mobile subscribers the lilac group operates in over  countries in latin america and the caribbean under the consumer brands vtr flow liberty más móvil and btc in addition the lilac group operates a subsea fiber network throughout the region in over  markets for more information please visit wwwlibertyglobalcom contacts liberty globalinvestor relationsoskar nooij    christian fangmann    john rea    orcorporate communicationsmatt beake    julia hart     recent stories liberty global to hold annual general meeting of shareholders june   denver coloradoeon enhanced online newsliberty global plc “liberty global” nasdaq lbtya lbtyb lbtyk lila and lilak will be holding its  annual general meeting of shareholders on more » liberty global to present at the th annual goldman sachs european cable  convergence conference june   denver coloradoeon enhanced o